token_info.name: Book of Changes
token_info.description: My personal take on the Book of Changes, or the I Ching (or many other names). This is not a translation, rather I have just written my interpretation based on years of use and reading of various English translations and commentaries. This is essentially a port of my Android app: "Uncomplicated I Ching". It's not meant to have any validity, it's primarily for personal use. Also the font is my handwriting. I'm making it available on request via twitter, if you want one, just ask!
